title: 2 Dog Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local restaurant offering changing side dishes using seasonal ingredients. On the menu is a vegetarian selections section, which including several wraps, a black bean soup, a veggie burger, and a portabella burger. The building is an old house with great primitive artwork, mainly of dogs. Brunch on Sunday.
